<p>By filling out this form, you authorize SCPR to charge your credit/debit card or your bank account on an auto-renew basis, until you tell us to stop.  In order to convert your membership to become a Sustainer, you must currently be a monthly donor to SCPR.  If you’re not currently contributing monthly and would like to sign up as a Sustainer, <a href="https://scprcontribute.publicradio.org/contribute.php?refId=sustainers" target="_blank">click here</a>.</p>

<p>If you have questions about your Sustaining Membership, contact Ruth Calichman at 626-583-5129.</p>  



